        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;introduction&#34;&gt;Introduction
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synologyм—җм„ң м—¬лҹ¬ мқ‘мҡ© н”„лЎңк·ёлһЁмқ„ м„Өм№ҳн•ҙм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳкё° мң„н•ҙм„ң DockerлҘј м• мҡ©н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
DockerлЎң Jenkins лҘј мӮ¬мҡ©мӨ‘мқёлҚ°, Jenkinsм—җм„ңлҸ„ DockerлҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҙм•јн•ҳлҠ” мғҒнҷ©мқҙ мғқкІЁ м§„н–үн•ҳкІҢ лҗҳм—ҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
Synologyк°Җ м•„лӢҢ лӢӨлҘё Machineм—җм„ңлҸ„ л№„мҠ·н•ҳкІҢ м§„н–үлҗҳм§Җл§Ң, мқҙлІҲ м„ӨлӘ…мқҖ SynologyлҘј кё°мӨҖмңјлЎң м„ӨлӘ…н•ҳкІ мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;м„ӨлӘ…н•ң л°©лІ•мқҖ Hostмқҳ docker sockмқ„ кіөмң н•ҳлҠ” л°©лІ•мһ…лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;prerequisite&#34;&gt;Prerequisite
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Jenkins Container Using Official Image&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;progress&#34;&gt;Progress
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;мғқк°ҒліҙлӢӨ м–ҙл өм§Җ м•ҠмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. м°Ёк·јм°Ёк·јнһҲ м§„н–үн•ҳл©ҙ мүҪмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
DSM 7.2лЎң м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠён•ң нӣ„м—җ м§„н–үн•ң мһ‘м—…мқҙлқј, мәЎмІҳн•ң мқҙлҜём§Җк°Җ м°Ёмқҙк°Җ мһҲмқ„ мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;1-docker-sock-кіөмң &#34;&gt;1. Docker sock кіөмң 
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Synologyм—җ м„Өм№ҳн•ҙмӨҖ Docker sockкіј containerм—җм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•  Docker sockмқ„ binding н•ҳлҠ” мһ‘м—…мқ„ н•ҙм•јн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. &lt;br&gt;
м•„лһҳмқҳ лӘ…л №м–ҙлҢҖлЎң м„Өм •н•ҙ мЈјл©ҙ лҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;webPort&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:8080 -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;agentPort&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:50000 -d -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;hostJenkinsDir&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:/var/jenkins_home jenkins/jenkins:lts
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# мҳҲмӢңлЎң л“Өл©ҙ м•„лһҳмҷҖ к°ҷмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run -p 8080:8080 -p 50000:50000 -d -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v /docker/jenkins/home:/var/jenkins_home jenkins/jenkins:lts
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;н•ҳм§Җл§Ң Synologyм—җм„ңлҠ” &lt;code&gt;/&lt;/code&gt; directory м„Өм •н•  мҲҳ м—Ҷкё°л–„л¬ём—җ, SSHлЎң м ‘мҶҚн•ҙм„ң м„Өм •н•ҙмЈјм–ҙм•јн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
SSHлЎң м ‘мҶҚн•ҙм„ң Docker commandлҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•  мӨҖл№„лҘј н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/update_command_in_host.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1868&#34;
	height=&#34;860&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/update_command_in_host_hu_a127f913902b77e7.jpg 480w, https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/update_command_in_host_hu_ce09b41752a7248b.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;update_command_in_host&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;217&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;521px&#34;
	
&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;м Җмқҳ кІҪмҡ°м—җлҠ” мң„мқҳ мқҙлҜём§ҖмІҳлҹј containerмқҳ volumeмқ„ updateн•  мҲҳ мһҲлҠ” м„Өм •мқҙ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
к·ёлһҳм„ң м•„лһҳмқҳ лӘ…л №м–ҙлҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҙм„ң volume binding н•ҳмҳҖмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker container update -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v /docker/jenkins/home:/var/jenkins_home &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;containerId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;мқҙл ҮкІҢ ліҖкІҪн•ң volume bindingмқҖ synology web uiмғҒм—җм„ңлҠ” ліҙмқҙм§Җ м•Ҡкё° л•Ңл¬ём—җ, лӘ…л №м–ҙлҘј нҶөн•ҙ мһҳ ліҖкІҪлҗҳм—ҲлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ҙм•јн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker container inspect &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;containerId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;          ...,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;          &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Mounts&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;bind&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Source&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/volume1/docker/jenkins/home&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Destination&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/var/jenkins_home&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Mode&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;rw&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;RW&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: true,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Propagation&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;rprivate&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Type&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;bind&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Source&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/var/run/docker.sock&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Destination&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;/var/run/docker.sock&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Mode&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;rw&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;RW&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: true,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Propagation&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;rprivate&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;]&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        ...
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;мң„мІҳлҹј &lt;code&gt;docker.sock&lt;/code&gt;мқҙ м¶”к°Җлҗҳм—ҲлӢӨл©ҙ, м •мғҒм ҒмңјлЎң лҗң кІғмһ…лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
нҳ№мӢң docker container update лӘ…л №м–ҙлҘј нҶөн•ҙ volume bindingмқ„ н•  мҲҳ м—ҶлӢӨл©ҙ, мғҲлЎң containerлҘј л§Ңл“ңлҠ”кІғмқҙ нҺён•ҳкІ мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
м§Ғм ‘ н•ҳм§„м•Ҡм•ҳм§Җл§Ң м•„лһҳмқҳ лӘ…л №м–ҙмІҳлҹј мһ…л Ҙн•ҳл©ҙ лҗҳм§Җм•Ҡмқ„к№Ң мӢ¶мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run --restart &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;policy&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; --name &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;jenkins&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;webPort&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:8080 -p &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;agentPort&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:50000 -d -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;hostJenkinsDir&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;:/var/jenkins_home jenkins/jenkins:lts
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# мҳҲмӢңлЎң л“Өл©ҙ м•„лһҳмҷҖ к°ҷмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker run --restart always --name jenkins -p 8080:8080 -p 50000:50000 -d -v /var/run/docker.sock:/var/run/docker.sock -v /docker/jenkins/home:/var/jenkins_home jenkins/jenkins:lts
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;н•ӯмғҒ мһ¬мӢңмһ‘ н•ҳлҠ” мҳөм…ҳмқ„ &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://docs.docker.com/engine/reference/run/#restart-policies---restart&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;кіөмӢқл¬ём„ң&lt;/a&gt;лҘј м°ёкі н•ҳмҳҖмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
ліёмқёмқҳ н•„мҡ”м—җ л”°лқј м„Өм •н•ҙмЈјм„ёмҡ”.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;2-jenkinsм—җ-docker-м„Өм№ҳ&#34;&gt;2. Jenkinsм—җ Docker м„Өм№ҳ
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Dockerfileмқ„ мғҲлЎң л§Ңл“Өм–ҙ, DockerлҘј м„Өм№ҳн•ҳлҠ” мҠӨнҒ¬лҰҪнҠёлҘј мһ…л Ҙн•ҙмЈјлҠ” л°©лІ•лҸ„ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.
н•ҳм§Җл§Ң мғҲлЎң мқҙлҜём§ҖлҘј л§Ңл“Өкі  кҙҖлҰ¬н•ҳлҠ”кұҙ лІҲкұ°лЎӯкё°лҸ„н•ҳкі , volume bindingмқ„ н•ҙм„ң лҚ°мқҙн„°к°Җ мң м§ҖлҗҳлҠ” мғҒнҷ©мқҙлӢҲ м„Өм№ҳ мҠӨнҒ¬лҰҪнҠёлҘј м ҖмһҘн•ҙл‘җлҠ”кІҢ мўӢлӢӨкі  мғқк°Ғмқҙ л“Өм—ҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
(JenkinsлҘј м—…к·ёл Ҳмқҙл“ңн•ҳкұ°лӮҳ Containerк°Җ мӮӯм ңлҗңлӢӨл©ҙ, м„Өм№ҳмҠӨнҒ¬лҰҪнҠёлҘј мғҲлЎң мӢӨн–үн•ҙмЈјкёҙ н•ҙм•јн•ҳм§Җл§Ңмҡ”.)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;м•„лһҳмқҳ лӮҙмҡ©мқҳ мҠӨнҒ¬лҰҪнҠёлҘј hostмқҳ &lt;code&gt;/docker/jenkins/home/install_jenkins.sh&lt;/code&gt;лЎң л§Ңл“Өм–ҙ мЈјм—ҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;#!/bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;curl https://get.docker.com/ &amp;gt; dockerinstall &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; chmod &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;777&lt;/span&gt; dockerinstall &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; ./dockerinstall
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;chmod &lt;span style=&#34;color:#ae81ff&#34;&gt;666&lt;/span&gt; /var/run/docker.sock
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;м„Өм№ҳн•ҳлҠ”лҚ° мЎ°кёҲ мӢңк°„мқҙ кұёлҰ¬кёҙн•©лӢҲлӢӨ. кё°лӢӨлҰ¬л©ҙ, м„Өм№ҳк°Җ мҷ„лЈҢлҗңкІғмқ„ ліҙмӢӨ мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;3-лҸҷмһ‘-нҷ•мқё&#34;&gt;3. лҸҷмһ‘ нҷ•мқё
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jenkins ContainerмҷҖ Web UIм—җм„ң Docker commandк°Җ мһҳ лҗҳлҠ”м§Җ нҷ•мқён•ҙліҙкІ мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. &lt;br&gt;
мҡ°м„ мқҖ Containerм—җм„ң нҷ•мқён•ҙліҙкІ мҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker exec -it &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;${&lt;/span&gt;containerId&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt; /bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#75715e&#34;&gt;# мҳҲмӢң&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker exec -it f0f5398c9a62 /bin/bash
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;---
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;docker container ls --all
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;мң„мқҳ лӘ…л №м–ҙл“Өмқ„ мӢӨн–үн•ҳл©ҙ Containerм—җ м ‘мҶҚн•ҳмҳҖкі , мӢңлҶҖлЎңм§Җм—җм„ң кө¬лҸҷмӨ‘мқё Container лҰ¬мҠӨнҠёлҘј нҷ•мқён•  мҲҳ мһҲкІҢлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ. &lt;br&gt;
кө¬лҸҷмӨ‘мқё Containerк°Җ м—Ҷмқ„ мҲҳлҠ” м—Ҷм§Җл§Ң, м—җлҹ¬лҠ” л°ңмғқн•ҙм„ңлҠ” м•Ҳлҗ©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;мң„м—җк№Ңм§Җл§Ң нҷ•мқён•ҙлҸ„ л¬ём ңлҠ” м—Ҷмқ„н…җлҚ°, м ҖлҠ” нҳ№мӢңлӮҳ мӢ¶м–ҙ лҚ” нҷ•мқён•ҙліҙм•ҳмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;br&gt;
м•„лһҳмІҳлҹј Jenkins pipelineмңјлЎң мӢӨн–үн•ҙліҙм•ҳмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-shell&#34; data-lang=&#34;shell&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;pipeline &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    agent any
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    stages &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        stage&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#39;Run Container&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            steps &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                script &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;{&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                    // Docker м»Ён…Ңмқҙл„Ҳ мӢӨн–ү
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                    docker.image&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;(&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;hello-world:latest&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;.run&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;                &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;            &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;}&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;img src=&#34;https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/console_job.jpg&#34;
	width=&#34;1406&#34;
	height=&#34;1494&#34;
	srcset=&#34;https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/console_job_hu_cc2eb9b2822dca56.jpg 480w, https://korcasus.github.io/p/use-docker-in-jenkins-docker/console_job_hu_60b3703374bbb5a1.jpg 1024w&#34;
	loading=&#34;lazy&#34;
	
		alt=&#34;console_job&#34;
	
	
		class=&#34;gallery-image&#34; 
		data-flex-grow=&#34;94&#34;
		data-flex-basis=&#34;225px&#34;
	
&gt;
мң„мқҳ кІ°кіјк№Ңм§Җ лӮҳмҳӨл©ҙ, jenkinsм—җм„ңлҸ„ dockerлҘј л§ҲмқҢк»Ҹ мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳмӢӨ мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;conclusion&#34;&gt;Conclusion
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;DockerлЎң кө¬лҸҷн•ң Jenkinsм—җм„ң DockerлҘј мӢӨн–үн•  мҲҳ мһҲлҸ„лЎқ н•ҙліҙм•ҳмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. &lt;br&gt;
ContainerлЎң л§Ңл“Өм–ҙм§„ Jenkinsм—җм„ң Hostмқҳ Dockerм—җ м ‘к·јн•  мҲҳ мһҲкІҢ л§Ңл“ лӢӨлҠ”кІҢ, нҺёлҰ¬н•ҳкёҙ н•ҳм§Җл§Ң ліҙм•ҲмғҒмңјлЎңлҠ” мўӢм§Җм•Ҡм•„ ліҙмһ…лӢҲлӢӨ.   &lt;br&gt;
мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳмӢ лӢӨл©ҙ ContainerмҷҖ Hostмқҳ ліҙм•Ҳмқ„ мўҖ лҚ” мӢ кІҪ мҚЁм„ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҙмЈјмӢңл©ҙ, м•Ҳм „н•  кІғ к°ҷмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;лӢӨлҘё л¶„л“Өм—җкІҢ лҸ„мӣҖмқҙ лҗҳл©ҙ мўӢкІ л„Өмҡ”. к°җмӮ¬н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.&lt;/p&gt;
